{"tid":1417993,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［中文堂時間］希望大家唔會忘記咩係不割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:47:12.000Z","uid":115133,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d85749e72f1df069737e00a832607a7fec50e2a5","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"呢場運動已經持續咗一排，由一開始見完林奠開記者會會好嬲到依加已經wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於一直冇正面回應/反饋，所以手足會無助、會燥、會不耐煩⋯⋯完全係人之常情。<br />\n有部分手足就化身火系魔法師，然而引起為數不少人嘅反對，但每次反對者一出聲都會被回覆：「不割蓆」<br />\n咁係咪唔割蓆就=一言堂？<br />\n<br />\n世說新語德行篇：「管寧、華歆嘗同席讀書，有乘軒冕過門者、寧讀如故，歆廢書出看，寧割席分坐，曰：『子非吾友也！』」 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">把席子割成兩半，不與對方並坐，有斷絕往來的意思。 表示朋友間因志趣不同，令人不屑與之為友，以致感情破裂，互不往來。 比喻和朋友斷絕交。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果有人話玩火就係鬼、係二五，呢啲先叫分化！<br />\n但假若只係<ins>表達佢嘅睇</ins>法，e.g.玩火好似唔太好咁，根本人哋就冇諗過割蓆⋯⋯<br />\n無錯我哋係不割蓆不指責，但絕對有俾人表達嘅自由。<br />\n所以有意見唔怕講，但語氣要溫和唔係屌鳩人咁款；有意見唔怕聽，之所以行到今日係靠慢慢累積經驗。<br />\n<br />\n要永遠記得我哋追求緊嘅係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自由</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自由唔係唔俾人講嘢，而係尊重每個人講嘅嘢。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果心情真係難以平伏，可以loop下梁天琦《致香港人的信》，必有新覺悟。<br />\n<br />\n以下係我一個老師嘅msg節錄，覺得幾有啟發性。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>However, I think having different voices and opinions is what democracy means. <br />\nLook at the USA! They have constant arguments and they have Trump 🤷🏻&zwj;♀ <br />\nThat&rsquo;s how a democratic society should work, with people agreeing and disagreeing, with leaders that you love and hate... <br />\nKeep that in mind and try to strive through the hardship with all the mates around you. </em></span>"},{"pid":"3767657bc881b297e169710ef7e0509e4b916974","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:39:18.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"33e0f77136284ab81b4022d3017c77fa709b0b0b","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:41:19.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bc7b3c998a9c62985a8e76487d3b34147b641c9f","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"人生第一次十連能否達成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1"},{"pid":"998996dc5bb21ac1323aebf951dc26b596c14177","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:44.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c94f93eb4d883a715bc09f89e3ae31ef03d4c275","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"shit其實係咪開錯台"},{"pid":"7d90a5e63926fb4174d05effe79e20763d200496","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6a44207e611eb5a018e6046c534ef09959668de7","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"08cec406b20341e453606eb39a2704b1c7a2a7eb","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"39fb9977f19423e72cf18a2101e10c84ab660a42","tid":1417993,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6525b4085eae87d4c371761ec15d8149132b008","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"310e39b1f0cf9f3c78d6637cf569e06152f56967","tid":1417993,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6525b4085eae87d4c371761ec15d8149132b008","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"7"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c523d6757d232852e2b7da07b7e0edd1