 <br />\n推之前已經有幾下熄街燈 <br />\n當佢推到係宿舍個街口，突然開頭燈，之後街燈熄左，班狗即刻狗衝 <br />\n我係上面係完全睇唔到情況係點 <br />\n1. 太黑 <br />\n2. 有大光燈照住 <br />\n係好撚恐怖，啲狗係極速推到去龍翔道，完全睇唔到前線情況，唔知有冇義士被咬同人踩人出現，有冇前線手足報情況？ <br />\n<br />\n大家入黎討論<br />\n點撚樣算！！！！！"},{"pid":"46ec98f89f9147439ba9f2f12b07846319fa5257","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"話時話如果屋企深藍記得要定時搵人傾下計，排解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897da510b4d120a8706a7972df063b728c1d46f7","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"毋忘初衷"},{"pid":"1140572da6c7049ce3023d3eb5220f6fe56d6b89","tid":1417993,"uid":25582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe310b45e5169858aeee2077b2dc2db2fd0b6be9","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"唔好變成你最憎嘅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b62767e57b022ca03ed664f6bccbbd997e2b93f","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:54:48.000Z","msg":"每個人嘅意見都係意見"},{"pid":"982b151879cbf3c66e5bdb0620f6037cdc9d402a","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:55:19.000Z","msg":"有疑心係好，但唔好過份敏感"},{"pid":"c0ecd9baed7bae7a2261935f94ea1222e686ba6a","tid":1417993,"uid":73302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後落去係點就靠大家信任"},{"pid":"f9697d9dc6075231451669ff79cb3f9cc32d614f","tid":1417993,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;